cs213.photoAlbum.simpleview
Class CmdView

java.lang.Object
  cs213.photoAlbum.simpleview.CmdView

public class CmdView
extends java.lang.Object

The text-based interface. CmdView will parse the user's text inputs and call the appropriate methods accordingly. There are two modes of the text based interface: command line, and interactive mode. The two modes define which actions the users can perform. (list users, list albums, add/remove tags users or photos, get photos by date or tag, etc.

Author:
Gal
